					-
						Nest-like, bedewed with oil. Bear this our worship to Savitar who
						sacrifices rightly.
					-
				-
					Mandala 6: Hymn 15: Verse 17
				-
					-
						Here the arranging priests, as did Atharvan, rub this Agni forth,
