					-
						The man hath brought his hymn of praise.
					-
				-
					Mandala 6: Hymn 16: Verse 27
				-
					-
						These, Agni, these are helped by thee, who strong and active all their
						lives,
					-
					-
						O'ercome the malice of the foe, fight down the malice ofthe foe.
					-
				-
					Mandala 6: Hymn 16: Verse 28
				-
					-
						May Agni with his pointed blaze cast down each fierce devouring fiend
					-
					-
						May Agni win us wealth by war.
					-
				-
					Mandala 6: Hymn 16: Verse 29
				-
					-
						O active Jatavedas, bring riches with store of hero sons:
