					-
						What time the godless was the Gods' assailant, Indra they chose to win the
						light of heaven.
					-
				-
					Mandala 6: Hymn 17: Verse 9
				-
					-
						Yea, e'en that heaven itself of old bent backward before thy bolt, in
						terror of its anger,
