				-
					Mandala 6: Hymn 17: Verse 10
				-
					-
						Yea, Strong One! Tvastar turned for thee, the Mighty, the bolt with
						thousand spikes and hundred edges,
					-
					-
						Eager and prompt at will, wherewith thou crushedst the boasting Dragon, O
						impetuous Hero.
