				Mandala 10: Hymn 25
			-
				-
					Mandala 10: Hymn 25: Verse 1
				-
					-
						SEND us a good and happy mind, send energy and mental power.
					-
					-
						Then-at your glad carouse-let men joy in thy love, Sweet juice! as kine in
