				-
					-
						The mighty Lord of spoil and wealth, Strong Friend of all prosperity;
					-
					-
						He with light movement shakes his beard, lovely and ne'er to be deceived.
					-
				-
					Mandala 10: Hymn 26: Verse 8
				-
